## CHANGELOG

### v2.0.4 - 09/03/16
  - Minor bug fix
    - Fixed styles for vertical accordion when it's nested inside a horizontal accordion

### v2.0.3 - 05/11/15
  - New feature
    - Added a 'panel padding' option

### v2.0.2 - 03/11/15
  - Minor bug fixes
    - Linkable hash is now updated when a tab is triggered manually
    - Resolved issue with Firefox not creating custom style rules on external stylesheets

### v2.0.1 - 27/08/15
  - Minor bug fixes
    - Prevent scaling on page load if responsive set to false
    - Edge case with css rules

### v2.0.0 - 07/07/15

### v2.0.0a - 05-07/15
  - Colour schemes
  - Colour styles
  - Tab settings
    - Size
    - Font size
    - Font family
    - Custom tab colours
    - Custom tab icons
  - Panel settings
    - Scrollable (w/ customised scrollbars)